{"tid":2212760,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"兩款Bethesda作品依然係限時獨佔PS5","createTime":"2020-09-22T04:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T06:51:12.000Z","uid":159183,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a7789f63450a10756bb16982ae5b6a591a23eecf","tid":2212760,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"關於這個撼動遊戲業界的微軟對Bethesda母公司收購案，在此就不多做撰述，詳情可以看隔<br />\n壁Xbox版，跟PS5較直接有關的是<br />\n <br />\n微軟Xbox部門負責人Phil Spencer在彭博社新報導中證實依然將履行Bethesda旗下新作《De<br />\nathloop》和《Ghostwire: Tokyo》在PS5限時獨佔推出的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7odEt8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7odEt8.jpg&h=31809404&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqjMe2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqjMe2u.jpg&h=7ae535c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個收購案到底影響多少？<br />\n受影響的工作室：<br />\nBethesda Studios<br />\nidSoftware<br />\nZeniMax Online<br />\nArkane Studios<br />\nmachinegames<br />\nTango Gameworks<br />\nAlpha Dog Games<br />\nRoundhouse Studios<br />\n <br />\n受影響的系列遊戲作品：<br />\nElder Scrolls<br />\nTESOnline<br />\nFallout<br />\nWolfenstein<br />\nDOOM<br />\nDishonored<br />\nThe Evil Within<br />\nPrey Game<br />\nRAGE<br />\nQuake<br />\nStarfield Game<br />\n <br />\n當然以上這些只是目前所知的一部分，還包含未公開作品，微軟本家工作室一下子從10幾間<br />\n衝到20幾間，要知道這影響的是發行商與旗下遍及全球的工作室，而不是之前那樣只收一間<br />\n工作室，金額高達2000多億，整個收購流程應該會在2021上半年完成。"},{"pid":"2e95be595862176cd5a66da4afde61d7ca0c7389","tid":2212760,"uid":29787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"一開game出個Xbox標誌比班fanboy睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affbd46dfd072fcacc541b3a31b22700299bdcfd","tid":2212760,"uid":343268,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"119ca58546c16128f2b1046d59d78ee1db8f5c58","tid":2212760,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">PS5獨佔</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">Also available on PC</span>"},{"pid":"73f93b85851917d6fb300ee1f46f8fe32864af9d","tid":2212760,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"2020年佔唔到仲會睇到xbox 同ps互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDeath loop 到底玩乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86abccf0689dcd062b8414d343ec82ee2766a1d","tid":2212760,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"呢兩隻本身都真係also available on PC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784176ca1ae67a5b6e93177e4785811c3a603bb2","tid":2212760,"uid":21279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"冇上古6我理你獨唔獨佔<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d4030701f30440a14495fc23fe150fb9456c16","tid":2212760,"uid":12150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"遲d gamepass 走天下，ea game 又有，Microsoft 自己game 又有，仲有咁多工作室幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望做大左唔好好似ea 咁迫人食屎就好"},{"pid":"a16ef5a4e742edbe3b6b05cf41f37c0a9b4a4be0","tid":2212760,"uid":113944,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"D 軟飯任豚成日話索狗鐘意亂咁咬, <br />\n初頭都覺得 D 索狗痴撚線, <br />\n但睇耐左發現其實兩邊都一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一見到有位入即刻衝出去汪汪汪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a6f1a8fd1594eef8658c32e112570b8e4d42f7","tid":2212760,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quot